  "2026-04-03T11:59:56.638Z",codex-agent,"Mandatory closure checklist: (1) run linked targeted tests via pm test <id> --run; (2) run pnpm build; (3) run node scripts/run-tests.mjs test; (4) run node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage; (5) update touched docs (README/PRD/AGENTS/CHANGELOG/ARCHITECTURE as applicable); (6) add pm comment with concrete evidence/results; (7) close + release item before commit/push."
